flutter is a frame work for dart
it works with widgets
Widgets are : Appbar, floating action button, Text, etc
You can build your own widget


Stateful widget / stateless widget

void main() is a function
    they are code snip its
    {} surround the function body
    you can call a function

main is a special function name since its the starting function

Text = string
numbers = integers or floats
    float = 2.12
    integers = 2

a void function does not return anything

you can make functions return values with the return command

variables can store information
with the var command

extends








first code
class Person {
  String name;
  int age;
  Person(String inputName, int age) {
    name = inputName;
    this.age = age;

  }
}

double addNumbers(double num1, double num2){
 // print(num1 + num2);
  return num1 + num2;
}

void main() {
  var p1 = Person(inputName = 'Quinten', age = 17);
  var p2 = Person(inputName = 'Monke', age = 14);
  p2.name = 'Ruben';
  print(p1.age);
  print(p2.name);
  double firstResult;
  firstResult = addNumbers(1, 2.20);
  print(firstResult + 1);
  print('Hello!');
}
